extendedInfo.description: With the all new Church At Creeks End android app, you'll be able to connect with our Church on-the-go like never before! Take a look at some of the amazing features:-See service times and get directions.-View staff bio's and contact info.-Listen to or watch our messages - when your done you can share them with friends and family!-Find out about upcoming events and get turn-by-turn directions, weather and parking info and more.-Our Media Section displays photo galleries and videos of our church.-Find sermon resources, recommended reading, and more in our Store section.-Learn about our worship team and listen to the music we play through the 'worship' area.-The more section displays Small Group info, Devotionals, Online Giving, and you can even send a Prayer Request!
